<% content_for :page_title do %>
  Services | Connect Control
<% end %>


<% content_for :services_title do %>
  Control Systems Integration
<% end %>

<!-- BREADCRUMBS -->
<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title pull-left">OUR SERVICES - <%= yield(:services_title) %></h1>
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
      <li><%= link_to "Home", root_path %></li>
      <li><%= link_to "Services", services_path %></li>
      <li class="active"><%= yield(:services_title) %></li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- END BREADCRUMBS -->

<!-- PAGE CONTENT -->
<div class="page-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <!-- BOXED CONTENT -->
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <%= render "layouts/service_table" %>
      </div>
      <!-- END BOXED CONTENT -->

      <div class="col-md-9">
        <%= image_tag "testimonial-bg.png", alt: "more intro image", class: "img-responsive" %>
      </br>
        <p>Systems integration is a challenge that most producers eventually face. Knowing the many options available and having the know-how to apply them to your facility is an asset.</p>

        <p>We can provide services such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li> suggestions to optimize productivity and equipment efficiency </li>
          <li> design solutions for control or safety additions </li>
          <li> PLC/HMI programming </li>
          <li> PLC migrations </li>
          <li> remote internet service and networking solutions </li>
          <li> solutions for obsolete or damaged equipment </li>
          <li> solutions for expansion or additions to existing infrastructure </li>
        </ul>

        <p>From concept to installation, we can supply control and network documentation such as:</p>        
          <ul>
            <li>engineered electrical I/O drawings</li>
            <li>shutdown key or cause and effect diagrams</li>
            <li>logic and control diagrams</li>
            <li>process control network diagrams</li>
            <li>design base memorandum or control philosophy</li>
            <li>commissioning protocol</li>
            <li>equipment control data sheets</li>
          </ul>
                
        <p class="text-center"><%= link_to "Back", services_path %></p> 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- END PAGE CONTENT -->


